<div class="page text-section">
  <h1><%= t('pages.contacts') %></h1>
  <%= image_tag 'logos/logo-2.png', width: 400, alt: ENV.fetch("BRAND") %>
  <p>My name is <%= ENV.fetch("PUBLIC_PERSON") %> and I am the founder and primary developer behind <%= ENV.fetch("BRAND") %>. I'd love hear how you're finding the site. What works? What could be better? What should we build next? Let me know!</p>
  <div class="email"><%= mail_to ENV.fetch("PUBLIC_EMAIL") %></div>
  <p>We're still new, and there's lots to improve upon, and plenty of new features in the pipeline. Check out <%= link_to "GitHub", "https://github.com/#{ENV.fetch("GITHUB_ID")}" %> to see what we're up to!</p>
</div>
